Even the last few questions offered no option to explain the reasoning behind the answers.  I don’t want people to not have healthcare but I know a government run plan will mean substandard care for everybody and healthcare decisions in the hands of the government leaving patients and family members with less say in their care.  That does not serve our country well as a whole.  And in terms of the pesticide question you did not provide enough detail.  Are we saying ban farmers from all pesticides or just some?  What is the evidence with the link that shows this is directly causing illnesses and deaths?  How much more will we have to pay for food?
